{"tid":1395230,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人史無前例地團結 小弟感動都 喊咗出嚟","createTime":"2019-08-01T16:30:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-02T08:20:53.000Z","uid":241000,"like":28,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"0d4d17127c109509c3de570dcb015a4b388f74d4","tid":1395230,"uid":241000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T16:30:01.000Z","msg":"平時各行各業都係只會互屌互串<br />\n但係去到大是大非<br />\n原來香港人仲係好愛呢個家<br />\n都係唔想香港慢慢咁被消失<br />\n<br />\n去到今時今日<br />\n大家都願意為咗香港走出嚟<br />\n史無前例咁團結<br />\n我真係好感動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n可能今次係香港最後嘅希望<br />\n大家今日所做嘅嘢<br />\n將會喺歷史被記載<br />\n<br />\n所以<br />\n我哋一定要贏<br />\n香港人加油呀<br />\n<br />\n大家一定要撐住<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我愛你哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"082be5a25215f3b7bb7205b97dd2047c9d17ae6b","tid":1395230,"uid":241000,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T16:31:36.000Z","msg":"為咗香港<br />\n8月5號我會出嚟罷工<br />\n你呢？"},{"pid":"98d1d8cb299edee2318accf1b25ce711d746d5f4","tid":1395230,"uid":241000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T08:03:38.000Z","msg":"為咗香港，8月5號我會罷工，你呢？"},{"pid":"2855cc8971510af0880b1b18774653aaa9214753","tid":1395230,"uid":258362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T08:04:21.000Z","msg":"得。番。一。個。鐘。<br />\n<br />\nkill2#<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n「救人！」世紀最大救義士唯一方法 正式上線 第三波<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1395699\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1395699</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/f